CVS Id: $Id: CHANGES 15987 2008-04-07 15:23:21Z xfade $

Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completely new features.

2008-04-07 xfade
  + Add config options to disable RCS updates when caching ratings on object

2007-10-30 xfade
  + Added comment count caching on object
  + Added support for rating without comment
  + Added filter to show only non-empty comments (rating without comment creates those)

2007-04-05 bergie
  + Added notifications support (sends notification to author of entry being commented)

2007-03-30 bergie
  + Added ratings support
  + Fixed some Midgard 1.8 issues

2006-06-23 bergie

  + Midgard 1.7 support

2006-05-05 torben
  - Initial version
